---
title: Italian Falafels & Veggie Couscous with Garlic Sautéed Onions & Red Pesto Dressing
description: What's a quick and easy way to bring a rich and tasty flavour to a dish? Add our moreish red pesto dressing that adds an extra burst of
flavour with every bite! Teamed with warm falafel bites, herby parsley and roasted veggies, this dish is all kinds of yum.

